full_title: Red Wine Supernova by Chappell Roan
title: Red Wine Supernova

description.plain: “Red Wine Supernova” is the second track on Chappell Roan’s debut album, The Rise and Fall of a Midwest Princess, and was released as a single on May 19, 2023. Roan has described the song as the “gay girl version” of Oasis’ “Champagne Supernova”.
